{"tid":213521,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"港豬幾時懲罰老飯民","createTime":"2017-04-23T07:44:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T02:41:21.000Z","uid":106869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"73afed060fe0a4599e240b51321c55fc20775b31","tid":213521,"uid":106869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T07:44:02.000Z","msg":"補選就快嚟啦（港共司法部如無意外一定DQ青政）<br />\n班飯民已經開始磨拳擦掌爭凳仔<br />\n係單議席單票制非建制實贏硬既<br />\n只係邊個會去選<br />\n同埋有冇新飯民or本土派去爭埋一份<br />\n<br />\n最近飯民作惡多端（長毛玩小圈子選舉、盲撐曾俊華、不支援旺角衝突被捕者、回鄉遊樂團、胡志偉楊岳橋失言）<br />\n<br />\n通常飯民標準口號都係 力保關鍵一席 同埋 唔好益建制派， 港豬就會乖乖投票<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係好想知港豬們係咪繼續投俾佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df51aa09b75a027a50628deae425b0c0578f867b","tid":213521,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T07:45:01.000Z","msg":"港豬/老飯民 關係密切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa456587333865b8cacb624099544e19f544bd04","tid":213521,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T07:50:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常飯民標準口號都係 力保關鍵一席 同埋 唔好益建制派， 港豬就會乖乖投票</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如何破解呢句？"},{"pid":"fd0fbba2eec161efaab434cabc40e47dac13d926","tid":213521,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T17:24:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>通常飯民標準口號都係 力保關鍵一席 同埋 唔好益建制派， 港豬就會乖乖投票</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如何破解呢句？</blockquote><br />\n攬炒都唔益你"},{"pid":"51f6a3c8da05b13bb4326993dc86ed16cdbcf45c","tid":213521,"uid":895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T00:28:09.000Z","msg":"守住關鍵一席？表決關鍵時刻就缺席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d78526c297a359069404b9f335e9b1dd2d74154","tid":213521,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T00:40:57.000Z","msg":"撐埋呢次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla